Item description without its partner:

Wondrous item, uncommon (requires attunement)

Counts as a Silvered Greataxe +1
    Heavy, two-handed
    1d12 Slashing damage

This item was forged as a symbol of a dwarven and elven alliance. 

Item description with its partner

Wondrous item, uncommon

Counts as a Silvered Greataxe +1
    Heavy, two-handed
    1d12 Slashing damage

This item was forged as a symbol of a dwarven and elven alliance. When the weilder is within 30 feet of the Lake Forged Blade they gain the following benefits:

Your Dexterity score increases by 2, to a maximum of 20
You have darkvision out to a range of 60 feet
You have advantage on saving throws against being charmed, and magic can't put you to sleep.
You can speak, read, and write Elvish